cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.PL 

The paper discusses the performance of Spark based data analytics on a large scale-up server machine, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC) and database systems (cs.DB). The analysis of the impact of data volume on performance also involves software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper proposes memory management techniques to improve performance, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
